ibniz Institute for Tropospheric Research]]). According to the ''[[Journal Citation Reports]]'', the journal has a 2013 [[impact factor]] of 3.062.<ref name=WoS>{{cite book |year=2014 |chapter=Atmospheric Environment |title=2013 [[Journal Citation Reports]] |publisher=[[Thomson Reuters]] |edition=Science |series=[[Web of Science]] |postscript=.}}</ref>
